  "description": "The house edge is the mathematical advantage built into a [gambling game](../index.md) for the operator. It represents the difference between the true [odds](../../terms/odds.md) of an event and the odds at which the operator pays out, ensuring that the operator retains a percentage of all [wagers](../../terms/wager.md) over time.",
  "name": "house edge",
